description: [``botocore``] This release introduces the DeleteCapacityReservation API and the ability to manage capacity reservations using CloudFormation
[``botocore``] This feature allows users to start and stop event ingestion on a CloudTrail Lake event data store.
[``botocore``] This release adds Selective Execution feature that allows SageMaker Pipelines users to run selected steps in a pipeline.
[``botocore``] Added APIs to describe managed products. The APIs retrieve information about rule groups that are managed by AWS and by AWS Marketplace sellers.
